fmt=#title
A simple bullet list of page titles. 


(:if false:)
[[#title]]
(:template defaults order=title:)
* [[{=$FullName}|+]]
[[#titleend]]
(:ifend:)

(:pagelist group={$Group} fmt=#title count=5:)
AllRecentChanges
