fmt=#simplename
Simple bullet list of page names, without the Group name. 


(:if false:)
[[#simplename]]
* [[({=$Group}/){=$Name}]]
[[#simplenameend]]
(:ifend:)

(:pagelist group={$Group} fmt=#simplename count=5:)
AllRecentChanges
AuthForm
AuthUser
EditForm
