fmt=#simplenamespaced
Simple bullet list of spaced page names, without the Group name. 


(:if false:)
[[#simplenamespaced]]
* [[({=$Group}/){=$Namespaced}]]
[[#simplenamespacedend]]
(:ifend:)

(:pagelist group={$Group} fmt=#simplenamespaced count=5:)
