fmt=#count
Number of pages in pagelist 


(:if false:)
[[#count]]
(:template defaults wrap=inline list=normal :)
(:template last:)
{$$PageCount}
[[#countend]]
(:ifend:)

Number of pages in the {$Group} group: (:pagelist group={$Group} fmt=#count :).

Number of pages in the {$Group} group: (:pagelist group={$Group} fmt=count :).

